These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, game, dunhill, ritmeester
1. the game-smoker is between the dunhill-smoker and the ritmeester-smoker##2
2. the game-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | ritmeester | game | dunhill |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, taxi, bus, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the taxi and the person driving the trike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Transport   | taxi | jet-ski | trike | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, boat, tram, train
1. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the boat and the person driving the train##2
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Transport   | snowmobile | train | tram | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, red, amber, white
1. the person who likes amber is between the person who likes red and the person who likes emerald##2
2. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
3. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Color   | white | red | amber | emerald |

 #################################

 
