2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in october##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |        1        |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Birthday   | october | august | april | march |

